      "bullets": [
        "Google DeepMind expands low-latency LLM options with 3.6 Flash and 3.5 Flash-Lite, targeting high-throughput, cost-sensitive production inference workloads.",
        "Gemini 3.5 Flash Cyber delivers a fine-tuned model specifically optimized for automated vulnerability detection, threat intelligence, and security operations workflows.",
        "The release highlights an industry trend toward domain-specific specialization and multi-tier model packaging for optimized latency and enterprise cost management."
      ]
    },
    {
