      "score": 34,
      "comments": 18,
      "author": "klingtnet",
      "published": "2026-07-20T08:28:45Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Native Git post-receive hooks enable lightweight, zero-dependency CI/CD pipelines directly on bare Git servers without external orchestrators.",
        "Execute automated test suites and deployments instantly upon git push by running shell scripts in isolated git worktree directories.",
        "Eliminates heavy SaaS CI platforms like GitHub Actions, reducing infrastructure complexity for simple self-hosted software projects."
      ]
    },
