      "bullets": [
        "Automated Linux Kernel CNA processes triggered a mass publication of kernel CVEs derived directly from stable patch commits.",
        "Vulnerability scanners face severe noise, rendering manual CVE triage ineffective for security operations and patch management.",
        "Security teams should shift from tracking individual CVE IDs to automating updates via upstream stable kernel releases."
