      "score": 45,
      "comments": 16,
      "author": "GLaDER",
      "published": "2026-07-21T10:11:59Z",
      "bullets": [
        "OpenSSH clients require matching .pub files alongside private keys to compute public key signatures during GitHub SSH authentication pre-flights.",
        "Missing .pub files break SSH key type detection and certificate matching, causing GitHub to reject valid authentication attempts.",
        "Audit CI/CD pipelines and developer environments to enforce ed25519 keys and ensure paired .pub files are preserved."
      ]
